---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Web Design Fareham | Professional Website Development" 
  description="Expert web design services in Fareham & Portchester. Custom WordPress & AstroJS websites for local businesses. Free consultation."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-50/30 to-primary-100/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Web Design <span class="text-primary-500">Fareham</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Professional website development for Fareham and Portchester businesses. 
          From the market town to the historic port, we create websites that help local companies thrive online.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-600 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg">
            Get Free Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+447850037850" class="border-2 border-primary-500 text-primary-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
            </svg>
            Call Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local Benefits -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Why Fareham Businesses Choose Us
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Local expertise for Fareham's thriving business community</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4H9z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Business Hub Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Fareham's business parks and tech sector need professional websites. We understand B2B 
            requirements and create sites that generate serious enquiries.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quick Turnaround</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Just 15 minutes from Fareham town centre, we offer fast response times. Most websites 
            completed within 2-4 weeks from consultation to launch.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Proven Results</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We've helped Fareham businesses across sectors - from tech companies to retail shops 
            and professional services firms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services for Fareham -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Web Development Services in Fareham
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Tailored solutions for the Fareham business community</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">B2B & Professional Services</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Fareham's thriving business sector needs professional, credible websites. We create 
            lead-generating sites for consultancies, tech firms, and service providers.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Lead capture forms
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Professional portfolio layouts
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Case study showcases
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">E-commerce & Retail</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            From the Market Quay shopping area to local independent shops, we build online stores 
            that drive sales and complement your physical presence.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              WooCommerce integration
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Click & collect functionality
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              Stock management
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fareham Areas Served -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Serving All of Fareham
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">We work with businesses across the Fareham area</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Fareham Town Centre</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Portchester</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Wallington</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Whiteley</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Park Gate</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Locks Heath</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Titchfield</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Stubbington</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Fareham Section (Unique Content) -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Web Design in the Heart of Fareham
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Serving businesses across PO14, PO15, PO16 and PO17 postcodes
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Fareham's unique position on the Solent coast, between Portsmouth and Southampton, makes it 
          one of Hampshire's most strategically important business locations. From the bustling Market Quay 
          shopping centre to the thriving business parks around Segensworth and Whiteley, we've helped 
          dozens of Fareham businesses establish their digital presence.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-10">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Portchester Castle Views</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Just like the iconic Portchester Castle dominates the harbour skyline, your website 
              should dominate local search results. We specialise in local SEO that puts Fareham 
              businesses on the map.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Segensworth Business Hub</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Whether you're based in the Segensworth business parks, the Fareham Innovation Centre, 
              or working from home in Locks Heath, we understand the B2B landscape here.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mb-6">
          Our Fareham clients range from marine services companies taking advantage of the creek 
          access, to tech startups at the Fareham Innovation Centre, to independent retailers 
          along West Street and the High Street. Each business gets a bespoke website that 
          reflects their unique position in the local market.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6">
          With excellent transport links via the M27 and proximity to both Portsmouth Harbour 
          and Southampton Airport, Fareham businesses can serve customers across the South Coast 
          and beyond. Your website should reflect that reach while maintaining strong local roots.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary-500 my-8">
          <p class="text-gray-800 italic">
            "Our new website has transformed how we connect with customers in Fareham and beyond. 
            Local enquiries have increased by 40% since launch." — Sarah M., Locks Heath
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 mt-8">Areas We Serve Around Fareham</h3>
        <p class="mb-6">
          From Portchester's historic charm to the modern developments at Whiteley, we understand 
          the distinct character of each area. We regularly work with businesses in:
        </p>

        <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Wallington (PO16)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Titchfield (PO14/15)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Park Gate (PO17)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Whiteley (PO15)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Stubbington (PO14)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.05 4.05a7 7 0 119.9 9.9L10 18.9l-4.95-4.95a7 7 0 010-9.9zM10 11a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Warsash (SO31)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mb-6">
          Ready to join the growing number of Fareham businesses with professional web presence? 
          We offer a free initial consultation, either at your premises or via video call, to 
          discuss how we can help your business thrive online.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to grow your Fareham business online?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8">
        Get a free consultation and transparent quote. Call <a href="tel:+447850037850" class="underline">07850 037850</a> or book online.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-primary-500 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg">
          Start Your Project
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+447850037850" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium text-lg">
          Call 07850 037850
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
